eria itakayokianzisha itakavyoelekeza.&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"mchakato-bodi-wataalam-hifadhi-ya-jamii-bima-waanza\",\"photo_url\":\"b125fcfa7d1aefe852fb08c918e284ef.jpeg\",\"created_at\":\"2022-08-25T17:17:44.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-08-26T09:35:06.000000Z\"}', '2022-08-26 06:39:43', '2022-08-26 06:39:43'),
