(2367, 1, 'News', 'store', '154.118.225.10', 'https://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Nukuu za Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi.\",\"title_sw\":\"Nukuu za Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi.\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">&ldquo;Shughuli nyingi za kiuchumi na kijamii zinazoendelea nchini zinahitaji sekta ya bima iliyoimara ili kuhakikisha maendeleo yetu ya kiuchumi yanalindwa&rdquo;. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Kwa kuwa masuala ya bima ni mtambuka na yanagusa Wizara\\/Taasisi mbalimbali ni vema yakashughulikiwa kwa pamoja badala ya kuiachia Wizara au Taasisi moja tu. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Ninaamini mabadiliko haya ya sheria yataendeleza ukuajia wa soko letu la bima kwani pamoja na takwimu za miaka sita kuonyesha kuwa soko letu linakuwa kwa wastani wa asilimia 7% bado ukuaji huu hauendani na mchango wa sekta hii muhimu katika pato la taifa; Hivyo ni muhimu mfahamu maana ya Sheria hii ya Bima ya lazima. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Serikali imedhamiria kutumia rasilimali zilizopo nchini ili kuboresha na kuinua uchumi wa nchi na mwananchi mmoja mmoja. Hivyo, tukushirikiana ili kulisukuma gurudumu hili kwa kuhakikisha shughuli zote za kiuchumi na kijamii zinakingwa na sekta hii ya Bima. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Tuwape ushirikiano EEAP ili waweze kutekeleza sheria ya Bima namba 10 ya mwaka 2009 na Sheria ya Fedha namba 5 ya mwaka 2022 inayoelekeza kuwepo kwa bima za lazima (mandatory insurance) kwa kujumuisha bima za masoko ya umma, majengo ya biashara, bidhaa zote zinazoagizwa kutoka nje, vyombo vya baharini na vivuko. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Watu wengi hudhani kuwa majukumu ya sekta ya bima huishia katika kutoa ulinzi dhidi ya masuala ya kiefdha. Sekta ya bima ina mchango katika uchumi wa kisasa na masoko ya fedha. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Kimsingi sekta ya inapaswa kuchangia kiasi kikubwa katika ukuajia wa uchumi wa taifa letu kwa kutoa utulivu katika utendaji wa biashara na kuzalisha rasilimali fedha za muda mrefu kwaajili ya miradi mbalimbali. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Serikali ina jukumu la kuhimarisha huduma kwa kuweka misingi imara itakayosaidia kukua huduma za bima nchini na kuimarisha mifumo ya kuwafikia wananchini wengi hususan ni bima ya Afya kwa wote. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">&ldquo;Shughuli nyingi za kiuchumi na kijamii zinazoendelea nchini zinahitaji sekta ya bima iliyoimara ili kuhakikisha maendeleo yetu ya kiuchumi yanalindwa&rdquo;. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Kwa kuwa masuala ya bima ni mtambuka na yanagusa Wizara\\/Taasisi mbalimbali ni vema yakashughulikiwa kwa pamoja badala ya kuiachia Wizara au Taasisi moja tu. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Ninaamini mabadiliko haya ya sheria yataendeleza ukuajia wa soko letu la bima kwani pamoja na takwimu za miaka sita kuonyesha kuwa soko letu linakuwa kwa wastani wa asilimia 7% bado ukuaji huu hauendani na mchango wa sekta hii muhimu katika pato la taifa; Hivyo ni muhimu mfahamu maana ya Sheria hii ya Bima ya lazima. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mhe. Balozi Hussein A. Kattanga.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Serikali imedhamiria kutumia rasilimali zilizopo nchini ili kuboresha na kuinua uchumi wa nchi na mwananchi mmoja mmoja. Hivyo, tukushirikiana ili kulisukuma gurudumu hili kwa kuhakikisha shughuli zote za kiuchumi na kijamii zinakingwa na sekta hii ya Bima. Katibu Mkuu