(2462, 5, 'News', 'store', '197.186.29.86', 'http://eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Hon. Eng. Zena: Board of Insurance Experts, Social Security, Statisticians Insurance key for Country\'s Economy\",\"title_sw\":\"Mhe. Mha. Zena: Bodi ya Wataalam Bima, Hifadhi Jamaii, Watakwimu Bima Muhimu kwa Uchumi wa Nchi\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">The Government is interested in ensuring that Tanzanians are benefitting from all sectors of the economy reforms in order to bring them sustainable development.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Hon. Engineer Zena A. Said, the Chief Secretary of Zanzibar Said this at the end of the week during the opening of the third meeting of stakeholders towards the establishment of the Board of Insurance Experts, Social Security and Actuaries held in Zanzibar at the University of Zanzibar (SUZA).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">The&nbsp;leader said &quot;The Government of the United Republic of Tanzania and the Revolutionary Government of Zanzibar together have a very sincere commitment to bring development to the people due to the major reforms that are going on in all sectors of the economy in the country&quot;.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">The Government has been providing various guidelines and instructions for creating a better environment to bring economic development to the people.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Speaking about the establishment of the board, Hon. Zena, said that this matter has come on time as it is in line with the Government&#39;s efforts to ensure that investments are productive in the country. She explained that &quot;This idea of \\u200b\\u200bthe establishment of a board of experts in the financial sector is important to us as the Government because it is in line with the Government&#39;s investment objectives, especially by increasing confidence to investors&quot;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">In addition, she instructed the committee of experts dealing with the establishment of the board to set plans and procedures that will reflect legal validity of the same. She said, &quot;Prepare an effective plan that will enable you to complete this important issue on time, follow all the procedures and laws so that this instrument has legal force&quot;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Initially, the Deputy Commissioner of Insurance Mrs. Khadija Said who is also the Vice Chairman of the Steering Committee for the establishment of the board told the Chief Secretary of Zanzibar that once the board is formed, it will be of great benefit as these professions will be recognized and have a positive contribution to economic development, it will also take into consideration the interests, skills and morals of its members. The CS emphasized that, &quot;The idea of \\u200b\\u200bestablishing this board of insurance experts, social security and actuaries is important now due to the growth of the financial sector in the country&quot;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">The third meeting meant to plan and discuss how to create the board, the technical committee had time to explain what has been reached so far. However, the next move will to be to carry out the study on the structure of the board by involving academics from various higher learning institutions, professionals, the citizens as well as learning from other boards like this one that is being worked on. The fourth meeting will be held in January 2023 to receive information and recommendations of the committee and finally allow other legal procedures to follow.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Serikali zetu zina dhamira ya kuhakikisha zinawaletea maendeleo wananchi kutokana na mageuzi makubwa yanayoendelea kuyafanywa katika sekta zote za uchumi nchini. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Hayo yalisemwa na Mhe. Mhandisi Zena A. Said Katibu wa Baraza la Mapinduzi na Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi wa Zanzibar mwishoni mwa wiki wakati akifungua mkutano wa tatu wa wadau<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">kuelekea uanzishwaji wa Bodi ya Wataalam wa Bima, Hifadhi Jamii na Watakwimu Bima uliofanyika jijini Zanzibar katika Chuo Kikuu cha Zanzibar (SUZA). <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Kiongozi huyo alisema &ldquo;Serikali ya Jamhuri wa Muungano wa Tanzania na Serikali ya Mapinduzi ya Zanzibar kwa pamoja zinayo dhamira ya dhati kabisa ya kuleta maendeleo kwa wananchi kutokana na mageuzi makubwa yanayoendelea katika sekta zote za uchumi nchini&rdquo;. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Serikali imekuwa ikitoa muongozo na maelekezo mbalimbali na kuweka mazingira bora ili kuwaletea wananchi maendeleo ya kiuchumi.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Akiongelea uanzishwaji wa bodi hiyo, Mhe. Zena alisema jambo hili limekuja kwa wakati kwani linaendana na jitihada za Serikali kuhakikisha uwekezaji unakuwa na tija nchini. Alifafanua kuwa <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\">&ldquo;Wazo hili la uanzishwaji wa bodi ya wataalam kwenye sekta ya fedha kwetu kama Serikali tunaliona ni muhimu kwa sababu linashahabiana na malengo ya Serikali kwenye uwekezaji hasa kwa kuongeza <em>confidence<\\/em> kwa wawekezaji&rdquo;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Aidha, aliiagiza kamati ya wataalamu inayoshughulika na uanzishwaji wa bodi hiyo kuweka mipango na taratibu inayoakisi uhalali wa kisheria. Alisema, &ldquo;Andaeni mpango madhubuti utakaowawezesha kukamilisha suala hili muhimu kwa wakati, fuateni taratibu na sheria zote ili chombo hiki kiwe na nguvu ya kisheria&rdquo;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Awali, Naibu Kamishna wa Bima ambaye pia ni Makamu Mwenyekiti wa Kamati ya Uendeshaji wa mchakato wa uanzishwaji wa bodi hiyo alimwambia Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi wa Zanzibar kuwa, bodi ikiundwa itakuwa na manufaa makubwa kwani taalum hizi zitatambulika na kuwa na mchango mzuri katika maendeleo ya uchumi ikiwa ni pamoja na kuangalia maslahi, weledi na maadili ya wanachama wake. Akasisitiza kuwa, &ldquo;Wazo la kuanzishwa kwa bodi hii ya wataalam wa bima, hifadhi jamii na watakwimu ni muhimu kwa sasa kutokana na ukuaji wa sekta ya fedha nchini&rdquo;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">Ikiwa ni mkutano wa tatu wa kupanga na kujadili jinsi ya kuundwa kwa bodi hiyo kamati ya ufundi ilipata wasaa wa kueleza mpaka sasa mchakato umefikia wapi. Hata hivyo, kinachofuata sasa ni kufanya utafiti wa muundo wa bodi hiyo kwa kuwahusisha wanataaluma kutoka vyuo mbalimbali, &nbsp;wananchi ikienda sambasamba na kujifunza kutoka bodi&nbsp; nyingine kama hii inayofanyiwa kazi. Mkutano kama huu utafanyika Januari 2023 kwa ajili ya kupokea taarifa na mapendekezo ya kamati na hatimaye kuruhusu taratibu nyingine za kisheria kufuata.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"42242b0f461e3bb1474364aada579f8c.jpeg\",\"user_id\":5,\"slug\":\"hon-eng-zena-board-of-insurance-experts-social-security-statisticians-insurance-key-for-country-s-economy\"}', '2022-10-31 07:08:49', '2022-10-31 07:08:49'),
