(2605, 1, 'News', 'store', '154.118.225.10', 'https://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Unganisheni nguvu kukinga majanga ya Afrika.\",\"title_sw\":\"Unganisheni nguvu kukinga majanga ya Afrika.\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.eeap.go.tz\\/uploads\\/text-editor\\/images\\/SDIGITAL 0658031993-10_1669964239.jpeg\\\" style=\\\"height:356px; width:500px\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Waziri Mkuu Mh. Kassim Majaliwa amezitaka kampuni za bima barani Afrika kuunganisha nguvu ili kutoa kinga dhidi ya majanga ya kiuchumi na kijamii.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Mhe. Majaliwa ameyasema hayo katika hafla ya ufunguzi wa mkutano wa kwanza wa Mamlaka za usimaizi wa bima barani Africa iliyofanyika jijini Arusha.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&ldquo;Nashauri wataalum wa bima muone umuhimu wa kuunganisha nguvu zenu kwa pamoja ili kuepusha upelekaji wa fedha za bima nje ya nchi pasipokuwepo na ulazima, kumbukeni Umoja ni nguvu&rdquo; alisema Mhe. Majaliwa.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Pia, amewataka kushirikiana kutoa kinga kwa majanga mbalimbali kwenye shughuli za kilimo, ufugaji, uvuvi na afya ambako majanga na athari yanaongezeka kwa sababu mbalimbali ikiwa ni pamoja na mabadiliko ya tabia nchi.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&nbsp;Mhe. Majaliwa amezitaka kampuni za bima barani Afrika kuendelea kutoa elimu kwa ili kuchochea uelewa wa matumizi ya bima barani Afrika.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.eeap.go.tz\\/uploads\\/text-editor\\/images\\/SDIGITAL 0658031993-34 (1)_1669965836.jpeg\\\" style=\\\"height:267px; width:400px\\\" \\/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.eeap.go.tz\\/uploads\\/text-editor\\/images\\/SDIGITAL 0658031993-18_1669965164.jpeg\\\" style=\\\"height:267px; width:400px\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&ldquo;Takwimu kuhusu uelewa wa bima barani Afrika zinaonyesha kwamba bado tuko nyuma sana na tunahitaji kuongeza juhudi na kuweka mikakati ya pamoja ili jamii ielewe umuhimu wa bima na kutumia huduma za bima kwa ajili ya maendeleo yao&rdquo; alisisitiza Mhe. Majaliwa.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Kwa upande wake Kamishna wa Bima Dkt. Baghayo Saqware amesema soko la bima nchini liko tayari kupokea wawekezaji katika maeneo ya kilimo, uvuvi na shughuli za bima mtawanyo.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Mkutano huu umewaleta pamoja wasimamizi wote wa sekta ya bima barani Afrika kwa ajili ya kujadili changamoto zinazokabili sekta ya bima barani Afrika.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.eeap.go.tz\\/uploads\\/text-editor\\/images\\/SDIGITAL 0658031993-10_1669964883.jpeg\\\" style=\\\"height:356px; width:500px\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Waziri Mkuu Mh. Kassim Majaliwa amezitaka kampuni za bima barani Afrika kuunganisha nguvu ili kutoa kinga dhidi ya majanga ya kiuchumi na kijamii.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Mhe. Majaliwa ameyasema hayo katika hafla ya ufunguzi wa mkutano wa kwanza wa Mamlaka za usimaizi wa bima barani Africa iliyofanyika jijini Arusha.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&ldquo;Nashauri wataalum wa bima muone umuhimu wa kuunganisha nguvu zenu kwa pamoja ili kuepusha upelekaji wa fedha za bima nje ya nchi pasipokuwepo na ulazima, kumbukeni Umoja ni nguvu&rdquo; alisema Mhe. Majaliwa.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Pia, amewataka kushirikiana kutoa kinga kwa majanga mbalimbali kwenye shughuli za kilimo, ufugaji, uvuvi na afya ambako majanga na athari yanaongezeka kwa sababu mbalimbali ikiwa ni pamoja na mabadiliko ya tabia nchi.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&nbsp;Mhe. Majaliwa amezitaka kampuni za bima barani Afrika kuendelea kutoa elimu ili kuchochea uelewa wa matumizi ya bima barani Afrika.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.eeap.go.tz\\/uploads\\/text-editor\\/images\\/SDIGITAL 0658031993-34 (1)_1669965898.jpeg\\\" style=\\\"height:267px; width:400px\\\" \\/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.eeap.go.tz\\/uploads\\/text-editor\\/images\\/SDIGITAL 0658031993-18_1669965098.jpeg\\\" style=\\\"height:267px; width:400px\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">&ldquo;Takwimu kuhusu uelewa wa bima barani Afrika zinaonyesha kwamba bado tuko nyuma sana na tunahitaji kuongeza juhudi na kuweka mikakati ya pamoja ili jamii ielewe umuhimu wa bima na kutumia huduma za bima kwa ajili ya maendeleo yao&rdquo; alisisitiza Mhe. Majaliwa.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Kwa upande wake Kamishna wa Bima Dkt. Baghayo Saqware amesema soko la bima nchini liko tayari kupokea wawekezaji katika maeneo ya kilimo, uvuvi na shughuli za bima mtawanyo.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2c363a\\\">Mkutano huu umewaleta pamoja wasimamizi wote wa sekta ya bima barani Afrika kwa ajili ya kujadili changamoto zinazokabili sekta ya bima barani Afrika.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"7aff24c6cf1468f25330b49abf03e32d.jpeg\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"unganisheni-nguvu-kukinga-majanga-ya-afrika\"}', '2022-12-02 04:25:17', '2022-12-02 04:25:17'),
