(2747, 1, 'News', 'store', '41.59.84.77', 'https://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"18th Meeting of East African Insurance Supervisors Association (EAISA)\",\"title_sw\":\"Mkutano wa 18 wa\\u00a0 Wasimamizi na Wakuu wa Mamlaka za Bima kwa\\u00a0 Nchi wanachama wa Jumuiya ya Afrika Mashariki\",\"content_en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">From 30th March to 31st March 2023<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">,<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Uganda hosted the 18th East African Insurance Supervisors Association (EAISA). The meeting was organized and hosted by <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">the <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Insurance Regulatory Authority of Uganda. (On the picture: Left to right: is <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">the <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Commissioner of Insurance Tanzania, Commissioner of Insurance Kenya, Commissioner of Insurance Uganda, Board Chairman of Insurance Regulatory Authority Kenya, representative of Governor Rwanda, General Secretary ARCA Burundi)<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">The purpose of the meeting was&nbsp;to discuss how East African Insurance Supervisors can collaborate and<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">ensure that EAC insurance markets grow. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">On his part, Dr. Baghayo<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> A.<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Saqware, Commissioner of Insurance Tanzania, explained that East African Insurance Market has common characteristics <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">and <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">common challenges which <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">require<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> common intervention. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Furthermore, Dr. <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Baghayo A. <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Saqware <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">emphasizes<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> the harmonization of legal instruments and <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">frameworks<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">in order<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> to <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">create<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">a favorable<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> environment for investors as well as <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">work<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> strategically together to address challenges.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Mkutano wa 18 wa&nbsp; Wasimamizi na Wakuu wa Mamlaka za Bima kwa&nbsp; Nchi wanachama wa Jumuiya ya<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Afrika Mashariki<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">(<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">East Africa Insurance Supervisors Association (EAISA)<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">) uliofanyika kuanzia tarehe 30 hadi 31 Machi 2023<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> ambapo Uganda ilikuwa Nchi mwenyeji.<\\/span><\\/span> <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Pichani ni wakuu wa mamlaka za bima waliohudhuria mkutano huo.Kutoka kushoto ni: Kamishana wa Bima-Tanzania&nbsp; akifuatiwa na Makamishna wa bima wa Kenya,Uganda, Mwenyekiti wa Bodi ya IRA Kenya,akifuatiwa na mwakilishi wa Gavana Benki Kuu ya Rwanda na&nbsp; General Secretary ARCA ya Burundi. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Mkutano huo hufanyika kila mwaka na Lengo la mkutano huo<\\/span><\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">lilikuwa ni kujadiliana masuala mbalimbali hasa namna ya kushirikiana kuendeleza soko la bima kwa nchi wanachama.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Kwa upande wake, Dkt. Baghayo Saqware,aliwaeleza washiriki kwamba,nimuhimu kujadiliana na kushirikiana kwa sababu soko la bima kwa nchi za ukanda wa Afrika mashariki lina maeneo mengi yanayofanana hivyo hata changamoto na utatuaji wake vinaendana na zinahitaji juhudi za pamoja katika utatuzi wake<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"0d0223b64e86c31370c1254a962d4cb3.jpeg\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"18th-meeting-of-east-african-insurance-supervisors-association-eaisa\"}', '2023-04-05 07:26:02', '2023-04-05 07:26:02'),
