(2755, 1, 'News', 'store', '41.59.95.6', 'https://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority welcomed the Insurance Ambassadors.\",\"title_sw\":\"Mamlaka ya Usimamizi wa Bima Tanzania iliwapokea Mabalozi wa Bima.\",\"content_en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">The Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority (EEAP), On 06th March 2023 welcomed the Insurance Ambassadors namely Hon. Engineer Zena Said (right) who is the Chief Secretary and the Secretary of the revolutionary government of Zanzibar and Hon. Wanu Hafidh Ameir (left) is a Member of the National Assembly of the United Republic. Ambassadors met with the Commissioner of Insurance Dr.Baghayo Saqware standing from (middle), Deputy Commissioner of Insurance Khadija Said&nbsp;and Mr. Rajab Kakusa CEO of TANRE attended the meeting. The three Insurance Ambassadors including Hon. Japhet Hasunga (who is not in the picture) have started their duties to join hands with EEAP and insurance industry stakeholders in the area of awareness and advising the Authority as part of the implementation of the meeting of General secretaries held September 2022 in Dodoma. On his part, Dr.Saqware congratulated the Insurance ambassadors for seeing the importance of joining hands with EEAP to increase the development of the insurance sub-sector. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">EEAP for a Safe Insurance Market<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Mamlaka ya Usimamizi wa Bima Tanzania (EEAP), tarehe 06 Machi 2023 iliwapokea Mabalozi wa Bima ambao ni Mheshimiwa Mhandisi Zena Said (kulia) ambaye ni Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi na Katibu wa Baraza la mapinduzi Zanzibar na Mhe. Wanu Hafidh Ameir (kushoto) ambaye ni Mbunge wa Bunge la Jamhuri ya Muungano. Mabalozi hao wamekutana na Kamishna wa Bima Dkt.Baghayo Saqware(katikati) na Naibu Kamishna Khadija Said. Aidha Ndg. Rajab Kakusa CEO wa TANRE&nbsp;alihudhuria mkutano huo. Mabalozi wa Bima hao ambao ni watatu ikiwa ni pamoja na Mhe.Japhet Hasunga (hayupo pichani) wameanza majukumu yao ya kuungana na EEAP na wadau wa Sekta ya bima katika eneo la kutoa uelewa na kuishauri Mamlaka ikiwa ni sehemu ya utekelezaji wa kikao cha Makatibu Wakuu cha Septemba 2022 kilichofanyika jijini Dodoma. Kwa upande wake Dkt.Saqware amewapongeza Mabolozi wa Bima kwa kuona umuhimu wa kuungana na EEAP ili kuongeza kasi ya maendeleo ya Sekta ndogo ya Bima.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">EEAP kwa Soko Salama la Bima.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"35c773df06ffc20c104dbaa4621ada06.jpeg\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"tanzania-insurance-regulatory-authority-welcomed-the-insurance-ambassadors\"}', '2023-04-08 03:30:10', '2023-04-08 03:30:10'),
