(2763, 1, 'News', 'store', '41.59.81.173', 'https://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority (EEAP) in collaboration with various stakeholders in the insurance, a fourth meeting\",\"title_sw\":\"Mamlaka ya Usimamizi wa Bima Tanzania (EEAP) kwa kushirikiana na wadau mbalimbali imefanya mkutano wa nne\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority (EEAP) in collaboration with various stakeholders in the insurance, social protection, and actuarial sectors held a fourth meeting to discuss the establishment of a professional board of Insurance, Social Protection, and Actuarial (ISPAB).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">The meeting was graced by Permanent Secretary Prime Minister&#39;s Office (Work, Employment, Youth, and People with Disabilities), Prof. Jamal Katundu as the guest of honor.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Prof. Katundu appreciated the Authority&rsquo;s efforts to take lead on the preliminary processes of establishing this crucial professional board. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">&ldquo;We have to act quick to have a board (ISPAB) that will oversee the rights and professionalism of the Insurance, Social Protection, and Actuarial experts since as per data we have the professions bring together above four thousand expert individuals but they have no a board that checks their daily conducts,&rdquo; said Prof. Katundu.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">On the other hand, Commissioner of Insurance, Dr. Baghayo Saqware insisted participants that it is the responsibility of all stakeholders to ensure that the board (ISPAB) is established for the benefit of all insurance and social insurance experts as well as the customers they save. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Stakeholders agreed to have a team from the participating institutions to be able to prepare a range of information that would facilitate access to the board of the ISPAB. The meeting was held as a continuation of meetings to discuss the establishment of the Insurance, Social Protection, and Actuarial Board (ISPAB) with the main agenda of presentating a proposal for ISPAB establishment, submission of the Terms of Reference (ToRs) for hiring a consultant, and the presentation on budget and resource mobilization.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Mamlaka ya Usimamizi wa Bima Tanzania (EEAP) kwa kushirikiana na wadau mbalimbali wa sekta ya bima, hifadhi ya jamii, na wataalam wa Takwimu Bima imefanya mkutano wa nne kujadili uanzishwaji wa bodi ya kitaalama ya Bima, Hifadhi ya Jamii, na Watakwimu Bima (ISPAB).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Mkutano huo ulihudhuriwa na Katibu Mkuu Ofisi ya Waziri Mkuu (Kazi, Ajira, Vijana na Watu Wenye Ulemavu), Prof. Jamal Katundu akiwa mgeni rasmi. Prof. Katundu alishukuru jitihada za Mamlaka za kuongoza katika mchakato wa awali wa kuanzisha bodi hii muhimu ya kitaaluma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">&quot;Lazima tuchukue hatua haraka ili kuwa na bodi kitaluuma ambayo itasimamia haki na maslahi &nbsp;ya wataalam wa Bima, Ulinzi wa Jamii, na watakwimu kwani kulingana na takwimu zilizopo kada hizi tatu zina zaidi ya watalaamu elfu nne lakini hawana bodi inayokagua mienendo yao ya kila siku ya kiutendaji,&rdquo; alisema Prof. Katundu.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Kwa upande mwake, Kamishna wa Bima, Dk.Baghayo Saqware aliwasisitiza washiriki tambua kuwa ni jukumu la wadau wote kuhakikisha bodi hiyo (ISPAB) inaanzishwa kwa manufaa ya wataalam wote wa bima na hifadhi ya jamii ili kuhakikisha wateja wanaowahudumia wanapata haki zao kwa mujibu wa miongozi ya kitaaluma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Wadau walikubaliana kuundwa kwa timu kutoka taasisi shiriki ili kuweza kuandaa taarifa mbalimbali zitakazorahisisha upatikanaji wa bodi ya ISPAB. Mkutano huo ulifanyika ikiwa ni mwendelezo wa vikao vya kujadili uanzishwaji wa Bodi ya Bima, Hifadhi ya Jamii, na Takwimu Bima (ISPAB) ikiwa na ajenda za kuwasilisha pendekezo la uanzishwaji wa ISPAB, uwasilishaji wa Hadidu za Rejea (ToRs) kwa ajili ya kuajiri Mshauri Mwelekezi, na uwasilishaji wa bajeti. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"9a60da1f9ebc73458a585e90d642a9da.jpeg\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"tanzania-insurance-regulatory-authority-eeap-in-collaboration-with-various-stakeholders-in-the-insurance-a-fourth-meeting\"}', '2023-05-15 02:59:56', '2023-05-15 02:59:56'),
(2764, 1, 'News', 'store', '41.59.81.193', 'https://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Tira establishes the Southern Zone offices.\",\"title_sw\":\"Tira yaanzisha kanda ya Kusini.\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Commissioner &nbsp;of Insurance Dr. Baghayo Saqware <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">paid courtesy to<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Lindi <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Regional Commissioner and the Of<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Region <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Police Commander <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Offices <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">in the Lindi Region to introduce the Authorit<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">y&rsquo;s<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Offices in the Southern <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Zone<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">.<\\/span> <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">In the visit Dr. Saqware was received by the Regional<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Administrative Secretary Ms. Zuwena Omary Jiri and Acting <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Regional <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Police Commander SAC. E. Kabaleki.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Dr. Saqware noted that the Authority&#39;s decision to open these offices is to ensure that supervision of the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">insurance<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">services <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">is<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> brought closer to the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">community<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">by<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> ensur<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">ing <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">that the insurance market reaches many people.<\\/span> <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Speaking about the presence of the Authority in Lindi Region Mrs. Zuwena congratulated the Authority for the decision as Lindi region is in the middle of Mtwara and Ruvuma regions which will make it easier for citizens to get services.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Also, Commander Kabaleki said the Police Force is ready to cooperate with the authority&rsquo;s <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">officials of the Southern <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Zone<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> to ensure that the insurance law is implemented.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">The authority has opened the South Zone Offices in Lindi Region which will serve Lindi, Mtwara and Ruvuma regions.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Kamishna wa Bima Dkt. Baghayo Saqware ametembele Ofisi za Mkuu wa Mkoa na Ofisi ya Kamanda wa Polisi Mkoa wa Lindi ili kutambulisha Ofisi za Mamlaka Kanda ya Kusini.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Katika ziara hiyo Dkt. Saqware alipokelewa na Katibu Tawala wa Mkoa Bi. Zuwena Omary Jiri na Kaimu Kamanda wa Polisi Mkoa wa Lini. SAC. E. Kabaleki.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Dkt. Saqware alibainisha kuwa uamzi wa Mamlaka kufungua ofisi hizo ni kuhakikisha huduma za usimamizi wa bima zinaso<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">g<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">ezwa karibu na wananchi na kuhakikisha soko la bima linawafikia wananchi wengi.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Akizungumzia uwepo wa Mamlaka katika Mkoa wa Lindi Bi. Zuwena aliipongeza Mamlaka kwa uamuzi huo kwani mkoa wa Lindi ni katikati ya mikoa ya Mtwara na Ruvuma jambo ambalo litarahisisha wananchi kupata huduma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Pia, Kamanda Kabaleki alisema Jeshi la Polisi liko tayari kushiriakiana na watendaji wa Mamlaka anda ya Kusini ili kuhakikisha sheria ya bima inatekelezwa.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Mamlaka imefungua Ofisi za Kanda ya Kusini Mkoani Lindi ambayo itahudumia mikoa ya Lindi, Mtwara na Ruvuma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"b63f6a233e6b709247edd2a59eae377d.jpeg\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"eeap-establishes-the-southern-zone-offices\"}', '2023-05-18 12:46:12', '2023-05-18 12:46:12'),
(2765, 1, 'News', 'store', '41.59.81.193', 'http://www.eeap.go.tz/cms/news', '{\"title_en\":\"Tira establishes the Southern Zone offices.\",\"title_sw\":\"Tira yaanzisha kanda ya Kusini.\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Commissioner &nbsp;of Insurance Dr. Baghayo Saqware <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">paid courtesy to<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Lindi <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Regional Commissioner and the Of<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Region <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Police Commander <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Offices <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">in the Lindi Region to introduce the Authorit<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">y&rsquo;s<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Offices in the Southern <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Zone<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">.<\\/span> <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">In the visit Dr. Saqware was received by the Regional<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> Administrative Secretary Ms. Zuwena Omary Jiri and Acting <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Regional <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Police Commander SAC. E. Kabaleki.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Dr. Saqware noted that the Authority&#39;s decision to open these offices is to ensure that supervision of the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">insurance<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">services <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">is<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> brought closer to the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">community<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">by<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> ensur<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">ing <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">that the insurance market reaches many people.<\\/span> <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Speaking about the presence of the Authority in Lindi Region Mrs. Zuwena congratulated the Authority for the decision as Lindi region is in the middle of Mtwara and Ruvuma regions which will make it easier for citizens to get services.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Also, Commander Kabaleki said the Police Force is ready to cooperate with the authority&rsquo;s <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">officials of the Southern <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">Zone<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"> to ensure that the insurance law is implemented.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\">The authority has opened the South Zone Offices in Lindi Region which will serve Lindi, Mtwara and Ruvuma regions.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Kamishna wa Bima Dkt. Baghayo Saqware ametembele Ofisi za Mkuu wa Mkoa na Ofisi ya Kamanda wa Polisi Mkoa wa Lindi ili kutambulisha Ofisi za Mamlaka Kanda ya Kusini.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Katika ziara hiyo Dkt. Saqware alipokelewa na Katibu Tawala wa Mkoa Bi. Zuwena Omary Jiri na Kaimu Kamanda wa Polisi Mkoa wa Lini. SAC. E. Kabaleki.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Dkt. Saqware alibainisha kuwa uamzi wa Mamlaka kufungua ofisi hizo ni kuhakikisha huduma za usimamizi wa bima zinaso<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">g<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">ezwa karibu na wananchi na kuhakikisha soko la bima linawafikia wananchi wengi.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Akizungumzia uwepo wa Mamlaka katika Mkoa wa Lindi Bi. Zuwena aliipongeza Mamlaka kwa uamuzi huo kwani mkoa wa Lindi ni katikati ya mikoa ya Mtwara na Ruvuma jambo ambalo litarahisisha wananchi kupata huduma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Pia, Kamanda Kabaleki alisema Jeshi la Polisi liko tayari kushiriakiana na watendaji wa Mamlaka anda ya Kusini ili kuhakikisha sheria ya bima inatekelezwa.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#222222\\\">Mamlaka imefungua Ofisi za Kanda ya Kusini Mkoani Lindi ambayo itahudumia mikoa ya Lindi, Mtwara na Ruvuma.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"d0baa2ec3baad8de3d7a79640812a849.jpeg\",\"user_id\":1,\"slug\":\"eeap-establishes-the-southern-zone-offices-2\"}', '2023-05-18 13:04:50', '2023-05-18 13:04:50'),
