":\"who-we-are\",\"status\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-08-09T17:50:33.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-06-01T12:38:19.000000Z\"}', '2023-06-12 17:56:12', '2023-06-12 17:56:12'),
(2981, 1, 'Page', 'destroy', '127.0.0.1', 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/cms/pages/7', '{\"id\":7,\"title_sw\":\"Tunachofanya\",\"title_en\":\"What we do\",\"has_sidebar\":0,\"content_sw\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9\\\">Majukumu ya Mamlaka.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Kusajili kampuni za bima nchini;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Kusimamia na kukagua mwenendo wa kampuni za bima nchini;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Kushughulikia malalamiko ya wananchi dhidi ya huduma za bima;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Kutoa elimu ya bima kwa umma;&nbsp; na<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Kusimamia biashara ya bima na masula yanayohusika na bima kwa mujibu wa sheria.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9\\\">Kuhusu EEAP<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\">Mamlaka ya Usimamizi wa Bima Tanzania (EEAP), chini ya Sheria ya Bima Na.10 ya mwaka 2009, ni taasisi ya serikali&nbsp;ilioanzishwa ili kutekeleza majukumu&nbsp;ya kusimamia&nbsp;soko na kuendeleza biashara ya bima nchini na&nbsp;masuala yanayohusiana na bima kwa mujibu wa sheria ndani ya&nbsp;Jamhuri ya Muungano wa Tanzania.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\">Tunaowahudumia<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\">Mamlaka ya Usimamizi wa Bima Tanzania inahudumia kampuni za bima zilizosajiliwa, wadau wote&nbsp;na umma kwa ujumla wa bima kwa mujibu wa sheria.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>&nbsp;<\\/h2>\",\"content_en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\\\"color:#2980b9\\\">Functions of the Authority<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Registration of all insurance players;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Supervision and Inspection of all insurance players;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Handling insurance complaints from the public;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Conducting insurance awareness to the Public; and<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Supervising insurance business and for related matters.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Who we are<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">The Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority (EEAP), under the Insurance Act No.10 of 2009, is a corporate body with perpetual succession and a common seal established to provide for the functions and powers of regulating and supervising insurance business and for related matters in the United Republic. The Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority (EEAP), under the Insurance Act No.10 of 2009, is a corporate body with perpetual succession and a common seal established to provide for the functions and powers of regulating and supervising insurance business and for related matters in the United Republic.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt\\\">Who we serve<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\">Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority serves all insurance registrants and players stated by the law and general public<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"what-we-do\",\"status\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-08-09T17:44:46.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-06-02T07:41:42.000000Z\"}', '2023-06-12 17:56:15', '2023-06-12 17:56:15'),
(2982, 1, 'Page', 'destroy', '127.0.0.1', 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/cms/pages/15', '{\"id\":15,\"title_sw\":\"EEAP Establishment\",\"title_en\":\"EEAP Establishment\",\"has_sidebar\":0,\"content_sw\":\"<p>The&nbsp; Authority is established under the the Insurance Act No.10 of 2009 as Follows:-<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>There is established a body to be known as the Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Subject to the general supervision of the Minister,the Authority shall be charged with the responsibility of coordinating policy and other matters relating to insurance in the United Republic.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>The&nbsp; Authority shall be a body corporate with perpetual succession and a common seal and shall, in its corporate name, be:-<br \\/>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a) Capable of suing and being sued;<br \\/>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (b) Capable of borrowing money,acquiring and disposing of property ;and<br \\/>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (c) Capable of doing all other things which a body corporate may lawful do.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"content_en\":\"<p>The&nbsp; Authority is established under the the Insurance Act No.10 of 2009 as Follows:-<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>There is established a body to be known as the Tanzania Insurance Regulatory Authority.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Subject to the general supervision of the Minister,the Authority shall be charged with the responsibility of coordinating policy and other matters relating to insurance in the United Republic.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>The&nbsp; Authority shall be a body corporate with perpetual succession and a common seal and shall, in its corporate name, be:-<br \\/>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a) Capable of suing and being sued;<br \\/>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (b) Capable of borrowing money,acquiring and disposing of property ;and<br \\/>\\r\\n\\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (c) Capable of doing all other things which a body corporate may lawful do.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"slug\":\"eeap-establishment\",\"status\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-08-10T17:13:46.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-08-12T18:01:04.000000Z\"}', '2023-06-12 17:56:18', '2023-06-12 17:56:18'),
